****************************************************************
 SOK-CHK-SEC            SECTION.
*
     MOVE    20                  TO   JYO-F01.
     MOVE    ZAI-F01             TO   JYO-F02.
     READ    HJYOKEN
         INVALID
             MOVE   "INV"      TO   HJYOKEN-INV-FLG
         NOT INVALID
             MOVE   SPACE      TO   HJYOKEN-INV-FLG
     END-READ.
*
 SOK-CHK-EXIT.
     EXIT.
